00:03:46.240 --> 00:03:50.490
As a folklorist, he emphasizes
his interests in the power

00:03:50.490 --> 00:03:54.250
of human creativity
arts and social justice.

00:03:54.250 --> 00:03:58.280
And the notion of a truly
multicultural society.

00:03:58.280 --> 00:04:02.960
Today, Mr Sirah will be talking
