00:25:26.420 --> 00:25:29.690
And to work with our friends here
at the American Folklife Center

00:25:29.690 --> 00:25:31.440
at the Library of Congress,
to help preserve

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:33.810
and digitize years'
worth of archives.

00:25:33.810 --> 00:25:36.810
To promote storytelling, not
only as a traditional folk art

00:25:36.810 --> 00:25:39.060
but to further it as a
contemporary practice.

00:25:39.060 --> 00:25:40.830
And through our connection
