00:25:51.110 --> 00:25:52.410
And why do we do that?

00:25:52.410 --> 00:25:54.290
We do it because stories matter.

00:25:54.290 --> 00:25:56.590
And I believe they matter a lot.

00:25:56.590 --> 00:26:00.340 position:56%
Through storytelling and, in my
work, I have seen how we can give --

00:26:00.340 --> 00:26:03.090
