00:26:03.090 --> 00:26:06.040
We can give precedence to
historical accountability.

00:26:06.040 --> 00:26:09.870
To offer healing and reconciliation
to the oppressed and the afflicted

00:26:09.870 --> 00:26:12.790
in ways that open heart of
listeners and enable us to share

00:26:12.790 --> 00:26:14.390
